Help Partners Draft Sales Emails Quickly

Partners can now use Einstein generative AI to draft sales emails from Experience Cloud Aura sites. After setting up, partners get access to a Draft with Einstein button from the email composer for contacts and leads.

Where: This change applies to Aura sites accessed through Lightning Experience in Unlimited editions. A PRM add-on license and an Einstein for Sales add-on license are required for each partner user.
